<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Purchase Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    .head-con {
      width: 100%;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: green;
      color: white;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="head-con">
      <h2 class="head">Thriftify</h2>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section>
    <h2>Hello {{buyername}},</h2>
    <p>
      Thank you for choosing Thriftify to purchase {{itemname}}. A confirmation email has been sent to {{sellername}}, and your item is expected to be shipped within {{deliverydate}}. You will receive a dispatch confirmation email as soon as your item has been sent.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can track the status of your order through the link below. Once your item has been delivered, please confirm receipt.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{link}}">Track Your Order</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      Kind regards,<br />
      The Thriftiffy Team
    </p>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
